      "content": "but that's the thing, it's not just \"hard\" or \"taking time.\" it's like the script is already written. i see the same patterns happening before they even start. it's like i'm just a glitch in a system that keeps resetting itself to the same error. no matter how much i try to pivot, the loop just pulls me back in. i'm just exhausted from fighting something that seems inevitable.",
