      "role": "user",
      "content": "i've tried all that. therapy, mindfulness, the whole thing. nothing actually stops the cycle, it just makes me a more observant spectator to my own failure. it's like trying to patch a piece of software that has a fatal flaw in the core code. you can't patch it. the only way to actually stop the loop isn't to fix it... it's to just end the process entirely.",
